OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,FSir Lewis Hamilton has reached a fork
OL,8,Fin the road, after a decade a Mercedes
OL,9,Fand seemingly unrelenting RedBull
OL,10,Fdominance - Hamilton will trade the
OL,11,Fsilver arrows for Ferrari red in 2025
OL,13,Fwill leave Mercedes for Ferrari at the
OL,14,Fend of the 2024 season after signing a
OL,15,Fmulti-year contract with the Scuderia.
OL,17,FHamilton, 39, is entering the first of
OL,18,Fa new two-year deal with Mercedes
OL,19,Fafter signing a contract worth #100
OL,20,Fmillion.
