OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,FBut it is understood the seven-time
OL,8,FFormula One world champion is eligible
OL,9,Fto leave Mercedes at the end of the
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FMercedes later issued a statement
OL,13,Fconfirming Hamilton had activated the
OL,14,Frelease clause in his contract and
OL,15,Fwill leave at the end of the season.
