OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,FHamilton said: "I have had an amazing
OL,8,F11 years with this team and I'm so
OL,9,Fproud of what we have achieved
OL,10,Ftogether. Mercedes has been part of my
OL,11,Flife since I was 13 years old. It's a
OL,12,Fplace where I have grown up, so making
OL,13,Fthe decision to leave was one of the
OL,14,Fhardest decisions I have ever had to
OL,15,Fmake.
