OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,F"But the time is right for me to take
OL,8,Fthis step and I'm excited to be taking
OL,9,Fon a new challenge. I will be forever
OL,10,Fgrateful for the incredible support of
OL,11,Fmy Mercedes family, especially Toto
OL,12,F(Wolff) for his friendship and
OL,13,Fleadership and I want to finish on a
OL,14,Fhigh together.
OL,16,F"I am 100 per cent committed to
OL,17,Fdelivering the best performance I can
OL,18,Fthis season and making my last year
OL,19,Fwith the Silver Arrows one to
OL,20,Fremember."
