OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,FMercedes team principal Wolff added:
OL,8,F"In terms of a team-driver pairing,
OL,9,Four relationship with Lewis has become
OL,10,Fthe most successful the sport has
OL,11,Fseen, and that's something we can look
OL,12,Fback on with pride; Lewis will always
OL,13,Fbe an important part of Mercedes
OL,14,Fmotorsport history.
OL,16,F"However, we knew our partnership
OL,17,Fwould come to a natural end at some
OL,18,Fpoint, and that day has now come. We
OL,19,Faccept Lewis' decision to seek a fresh
OL,20,Fchallenge, and our opportunities for
OL,21,Fthe future are exciting to contemplate.
