OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,F"But for now, we still have one season
OL,8,Fto go, and we are focused on going
OL,9,Fracing to deliver a strong 2024."
OL,11,FThe move ends an extraordinarily
OL,12,Fsuccessful partnership. Hamilton won
OL,13,Fsix of his world titles with Mercedes
OL,14,Fin the space of seven years from 2014-
OL,15,F20.
OL,17,FHowever, the team have since fallen
OL,18,Foff the pace and Hamilton has not won
OL,19,Fa race since narrowly missing out on a
OL,20,Frecord eighth world championship in
OL,21,F2021.
