OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,FHamilton will take on a vacancy likely
OL,8,Fmade by Carlos Sainz, whose contract
OL,9,Fis due to expire at the end of the
OL,10,Fcurrent year.
OL,12,FFerrari's other driver, Charles
OL,13,FLeclerc, recently agreed a new long-
OL,14,Fterm deal.
OL,16,FIt is not the first time Hamilton has
OL,17,Fbeen linked with Ferrari, with rumours
OL,18,Fof a potential move prior to him
OL,19,Fsigning his most recent Mercedes
OL,20,Fcontract last year.
