OL,3,CLewis Hamilton officially leaving
OL,4,CMercedes for Ferrari at the end of
OL,5,C2024 season
OL,7,FHamilton began his Formula One career
OL,8,Fwith McLaren and won his first world
OL,9,Ftitle with them in 2008 before
OL,10,Fswitching to Mercedes in 2013.
OL,12,FIn terms of race wins, he is the most
OL,13,Fsuccessful driver in the sport's
OL,14,Fhistory with 103, 12 ahead of Michael
OL,15,FSchumacher, with whom he shares the
OL,16,Frecord for the most world titles.
OL,18,FThe Formula One season begins on
OL,19,FFebruary 28 at the Bahrain Grand Prix.
